<!-- SECTIE 17 — FAQ                        -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div style="background:#FAF8F2; padding:72px 20px;">
  <div style="max-width:760px; margin:0 auto;">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px;">
      <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#C9A84C; margin:0 0 14px 0;">
        QUICK ANSWERS
      </p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif; font-weight:800; font-size:clamp(24px,5vw,32px); color:#0A0A0A; line-height:1.2; margin:0 0 12px 0;">
        The Questions Every Man Asks First.
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; color:#777; margin:0 auto; max-width:440px; line-height:1.6;">
        We built this for skeptics. Short answers here. 121 questions on the full FAQ page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ ITEMS -->
    <div style="border-top:1px solid #e8e0d0;">

      <!-- Q1 -->
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d0;">
        <summary style="padding:22px 0; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#0A0A0A; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;">
          "How is this different from a regular testosterone booster?"
          <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-size:20px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:300;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div style="padding:0 0 24px; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666; line-height:1.8;">
          Most T-boosters go straight to Step 4 and hope for the best. We start at Step 1: <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">thyroid optimization.</strong> Your thyroid converts T4 into active T3 — the master switch that controls your entire hormone cascade. Without optimal T3, no amount of zinc or ashwagandha will fully work. We fix the bottleneck first. <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-weight:600;">Different mechanism. Different results.</span>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q2 -->
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d0;">
        <summary style="padding:22px 0; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#0A0A0A; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;">
          "What if it doesn't work for me?"
          <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-size:20px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:300;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div style="padding:0 0 24px; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666; line-height:1.8;">
          <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">90-Day Money-Back Guarantee.</strong> Full refund. No phone calls. No retention scripts. No hoops. Follow the T3 Protocol for 90 days — if you don't feel the shift, email us and we refund every cent. We have a refund button. That's it.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q3 -->
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d0;">
        <summary style="padding:22px 0; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#0A0A0A; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;">
          "What are my options?"
          <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-size:20px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:300;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div style="padding:0 0 24px; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666; line-height:1.8;">
          One-time purchase starting at <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">$49.99</strong> — no commitment, no strings. Or subscribe to the T3 Protocol starting from <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">$39.99/mo</strong> — free shipping, Foundation Academy included, bigger savings on bundles. Cancel in 2 clicks, anytime. No phone call required.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q4 -->
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d0;">
        <summary style="padding:22px 0; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#0A0A0A; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;">
          "How fast will I feel a difference?"
          <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-size:20px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:300;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div style="padding:0 0 24px; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666; line-height:1.8;">
          <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">Week 1–2:</strong> Energy returns. Sleep improves. The fog starts lifting. <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">Week 3–4:</strong> Drive comes back. Focus sharpens. She notices before you do. <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">Month 3:</strong> Blood work confirms it. Most men in this window are up <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-weight:600;">30–42% in total testosterone.</span>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q5 -->
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d0;">
        <summary style="padding:22px 0; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#0A0A0A; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;">
          "Can I take this with my medications?"
          <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-size:20px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:300;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div style="padding:0 0 24px; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666; line-height:1.8;">
          We always recommend consulting your doctor first — especially if you take blood thinners, thyroid medication, or diabetes medication. <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">Every ingredient and every milligram is on the label. No proprietary blends.</strong> Show your doctor the full formula. We're transparent about every dose specifically so you can have that conversation without guessing.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q6 -->
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d0;">
        <summary style="padding:22px 0; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#0A0A0A; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;">
          "Why haven't I heard of the T3 connection before?"
          <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-size:20px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:300;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div style="padding:0 0 24px; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666; line-height:1.8;">
          Two reasons. First: <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">the supplement industry makes more money selling you Step 4 products</strong> — zinc, tribulus, ashwagandha — in separate bottles. There's no incentive to fix Step 1 and consolidate everything. Second: <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">you can't patent a thyroid pathway.</strong> Nobody owns it, so nobody funds the marketing. The science has been there for decades. The industry just ignores it.
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Q7 -->
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d0;">
        <summary style="padding:22px 0; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#0A0A0A; cursor:pointer; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;">
          "Is this for me if I'm over 60?"
          <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-size:20px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:300;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div style="padding:0 0 24px; font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#666; line-height:1.8;">
          <strong style="color:#0A0A0A;">Yes.</strong> Customer #31 went from 570 to 703 ng/dL at age 72 — <span style="color:#C9A84C; font-weight:600;">+23%.</span> Verified customers at 63, 67, 69, 72, 73, and 75. No stimulants. No synthetic hormones. If anything, older men often see the most dramatic improvements — because the T3 bottleneck has been building longer. Show the full label to your doctor before you start.
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>

